<P>__{(pointing)}
<D>__{but eventually, i'm going to be in that position.}
<A>__{gail gets up from her chair. she walks past mickey to a nearby cabinet. she opens a drawer, rummaging around for something. the camera follows her, leaving mickey briefly.}
